Tendios is an AI-native B2B SaaS that goes beyond search to do the work for you. Powered by Digital Workers coordinated through Agentic Workflows, it streamlines every step of winning public tenders.

Autonomous agents monitor official sources 24/7, enrich and de-duplicate data, and surface relevant tenders with advanced filters and custom alerts. Real-time notifications mean you never miss a deadline.

Teams collaborate in one place: share tenders, assign tasks, track progress, and control approvals while Agentic Workflows handle hand-offs between people and bots.

Ask natural-language questions about any tender, run compliance and eligibility checks, and auto-extract requirements. Digital Workers draft structured bids, tailor answers, pre-fill forms, and validate against mandatory criteria—accelerating proposals and improving win rates.

With AI, Digital Workers, and auditable automation, Tendios makes tender management faster, smarter, and reliably consistent.

company_description:

The platform combines the reach of a B2C brand with the efficiency of B2B-like distribution, powered by a creative go-to-market engine called The Mesh Engine - a peer-powered alternative to paid advertising.

Traction to date: €1.8M in revenue, 2,200+ travelers from 40+ countries, and a 4.8/5 public rating across 400+ reviews. In 2025, the company is on track to land between €1M and €1.2M in revenue.

Currently raising a €3M Seed+ round to productivize its go-to-market strategy by building scraping algorithms, AI agents, and custom software to automate 99% of operations. €2M already committed by 2 VCs.
